# Emerge Social Architecture — Revised Production Plan

## Architecture Pivot Summary

| Concept | Old (Broken) | New (Production) |
|---------|-------------|------------------|
| **Clubs** | User-created tribes | 5 fixed archetype clubs (Athlete, Scholar, Creator, Stoic, Zealot) |
| **Challenges** | Generic, unfiltered | Archetype-based — filtered to user's identity |
| **Friends** | Generic friend list | Accountability Partners with Social Contracts |
| **Create flows** | FABs for "Create Club" / "Create Challenge" | **Removed entirely** |

### The 5 Archetype Clubs (Fixed)
| Club | Tagline | Color |
|------|---------|-------|
| The Athletes | "Strength through discipline" | `#FF5252` |
| The Scholars | "Knowledge is power" | `#7C3AED` |
| The Creators | "Make something today" | `#FFD700` |
| The Stoics | "Master your mind" | `#26A69A` |
| The Zealots | "Passion through unwavering faith" | `#991B1B` |

Users auto-join the club matching their archetype on signup. The Clubs tab shows your archetype club's stats, top contributors, and archetype-specific activity.

---

## Proposed Changes — 6 Phases

### Phase 1: Remove Create Flows + Seed Archetype Clubs

> **Goal**: Delete user-created tribe/challenge flows. Replace with fixed archetype clubs.

#### [DELETE] [create_tribe_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/presentation/screens/create_tribe_screen.dart)
Remove entirely — clubs are fixed archetype-based, not user-created.

#### [MODIFY] [community_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/presentation/screens/community_screen.dart)
- Remove FAB entirely (`_buildFab()` method + `floatingActionButton` property)
- Remove `_createClub()` method and its Level 5 gate
- Remove import of [create_tribe_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/presentation/screens/create_tribe_screen.dart)
- Replace [_buildClubsTab()](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/presentation/screens/community_screen.dart#164-228) — instead of `ref.watch(tribesProvider)`, show the user's archetype club directly using `userStatsStreamProvider` → `profile.archetype` → `ArchetypeTheme.forArchetype()`
- Remove "Create First Club" empty state — user always has a club (their archetype)

#### [MODIFY] [tribe_repository.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/data/repositories/tribe_repository.dart)
- Remove [createTribe()](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/data/repositories/tribe_repository.dart#49-54) method
- Add [getArchetypeClub(UserArchetype archetype)](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/data/repositories/tribe_repository.dart#8-9) — fetches the fixed club for the archetype
- Keep [joinTribe()](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/data/repositories/tribe_repository.dart#56-80) / [leaveTribe()](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/data/repositories/tribe_repository.dart#82-104) (used for auto-join on archetype selection)

#### [MODIFY] [tribes_provider.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/presentation/providers/tribes_provider.dart)
- Replace `tribesProvider` with `userClubProvider` — returns the single club for the user's archetype
- Add `clubContributorsProvider(archetype)` — top XP earners in that archetype club
- Add `clubActivityProvider(archetype)` — recent activity in the club

