## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
```
flutter test test/features/gamification/domain/services/gamification_service_test.dart
flutter test test/features/gamification/integration/level_progression_test.dart
flutter test test/features/gamification/domain/services/reward_service_test.dart  # NEW
flutter analyze
```

### Manual Verification
1. **Clubs tab**: Shows user's archetype club automatically (no "Create" button)
2. **Challenges tab**: Shows archetype-filtered challenges from Firestore (no hardcoded data)
3. **Partners tab**: Shows real accountability partners, pending requests, active contracts
4. **Leaderboard**: Partners display titles and styled nameplates

> [!WARNING]
> Phase 6 (consumable IAP) requires RevenueCat dashboard configuration. Code ready, E2E testing requires sandbox.

