### Phase 8: Solo Challenge Creation

> **Goal**: Allow users to create custom solo challenges for themselves, adhering to the "only solo individuals" constraint.

#### [MODIFY] [challenge_repository.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/data/repositories/challenge_repository.dart)
- Add abstract method: `Future<void> createSoloChallenge(String userId, Challenge challenge);`
- Implement it in [FirestoreChallengeRepository](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/data/repositories/challenge_repository.dart#12-131) to save the generated [Challenge](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/domain/entities/social_entities.dart#17-36) directly into the user's `users/{userId}/challenges` subcollection so it appears immediately in their active quests.

#### [NEW] [create_solo_challenge_dialog.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/presentation/screens/create_solo_challenge_dialog.dart)
- A streamlined, floating dialog mimicking the `AdvancedCreateHabitScreen` aesthetic.
- Fields: Title, Description, Category (Fitness, Mindfulness, etc.), Duration (7, 14, 21, 30 days).
- Automatically initializes the [Challenge](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/domain/entities/social_entities.dart#17-36) object with `isTeamChallenge = false`, generates placeholder/template steps based on duration, and calls the repository to save.

#### [MODIFY] [challenges_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/HP/Downloads/emerge_app/lib/features/social/presentation/screens/challenges_screen.dart)
- Add a FloatingActionButton (FAB) with a "+" icon.
- Tapping the FAB opens the `CreateSoloChallengeDialog`.
